yangzhanbozh@umass.edu.comment: I like the rooms. They are spacious and the desks are honestly the best things in these dorms. I gave it a 3 because I hated the bathrooms. 2 showers share a changing room and they are only separated by curtains. If you want lots of privacy you would not like these bathrooms!
